data.description: Come and see this adorable 3 bedroom 1 and 1/2 bath ranch home!  As you enter the home, you will find an eat-in kitchen that leads into the living room with a vaulted ceiling.  There are hardwood floors throughout the home.  The half bath is attached to the primary bedroom.  You will find the laundry room in the back of the garage which is temperature controlled.  The large back yard is fully fenced in and perfect for backyard entertaining!
